HAL signals

* risc-jog-vel
    + HOST:
        . description: requested velocity for risc jogging
        . direction: INPUT
        . type: hal_float_t
        . velocity: unit/second
    + RISC:
        . parameter: JOG_VEL
        . format: signed 32-bit value
        . format: 16.16 pulse unit per servo-period
        . description: jog velocity for RISC-Jogging
